Name: Golden Gate Bridge
Description: The American Society of Civil Engineers has classified the Golden Gate Bridge as a modern-day Wonder of the World, and in contemporary times, it is one of the most internationally recognized landmarks in San Francisco and the state of California.

Name: Terracotta Army
Description: It is the tomb of Qin Shi Huang, the emperor of the Qin Dynasty in Chinese history, and the first large-scale, elaborately laid out and well-preserved imperial tomb in China

Name: Hawaii
